title: D-Rack

class: I/O rack

description: As recognisable as the consoles it supports, the DiGiCo D-Rack comes as standard with the SD9 and is available as an option on all SD-Series consoles.<br /><br />Providing 32 microphone inputs, 8 line outputs and 8 optional modular outputs that can be selected as either analogue or AES, the D-Rack provides a maximum capacity of 32 ins and 16 outs at 48kHz. The hum and noise of analogue multicores are eliminated courtesy of a digital Cat5e connection to the console work surface. When running at 96kHz on Cat5e, the D-Rack supports 28 mic inputs and up to 16 outputs.<br /><br />For full flexibility, optional 7U rack mount ears are also available alongside an extra PSU for redundancy and a fibre optic connection.
